---
title: Cal Smart Southwest Turkey with Fiesta Bean Salad and Lime Crema
description: This colourful salad is packed full of heart-healthy beans and crisp veggies, not to mention bold, fresh flavours! Be generous with your seasoning to give the beans extra oomph.

